full_text:
Interesting file. I hear a voice say "king" right before you say kingdom and "amen" after you say amen in the prayer. I also hear the Charlie, as well as the names phillip (repeated twice)and phyllis. When you ask about the ed I hear "he wants to speak" then near the end it spunds like you have a bird or something and last words on that clip after the bird noise I hear is "stop" "why the birds near us". 

Was that a bird?

Misty
